data.description: Motivated Sellers! Welcome Home to Your Dream Oasis with a Rear Fenced Yard, Oversized Paver Patio, and a Pool with Lanai and Beautiful Waterfall Feature! New roof and A/C too!Step into a world of comfort with this exquisite 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage pool home that offers so much more. With a den that can easily be transformed into a possible 4th bedroom, this meticulously maintained property boasts a new roof and A/C for your peace of mind.Spread over a generous 2,121 square feet, this home is designed to embrace the Florida lifestyle. The moment you enter, you'll be captivated by the large, open living room, which seamlessly connects to the outdoor paradise through a triple slider, offering breathtaking pool views. The vaulted ceilings add an extra touch of grandeur to the space.Ceramic tile flooring throughout the home adds an element of style and easy maintenance. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring an eat-in nook, plenty of cabinets for storage, granite counters, and a convenient breakfast bar for those quick meals on the go.For added convenience, an indoor laundry room with cabinets and ample counters for folding, along with a washer and dryer, makes daily chores a breeze.The master bedroom is a true retreat, generously oversized and offering an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower, dual sinks, and a relaxing garden tub, creating a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home.Outdoors, you'll discover the true highlight of this property - a refreshing pool with a beautiful waterfall feature that adds a touch of serenity and elegance to your oasis. The pool is complemented by a lanai, perfect for cooling off during those hot summer days. What's more, this home features a rear fenced yard, providing a sense of privacy and security, along with an oversized paver patio that's perfect for hosting barbecues, lounging with a good book, or entertaining friends and family. The patio is the ideal spot to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather while creating unforgettable memories.This home is not just a house; it's a lifestyle. With its desirable features, spacious layout, and a location that offers easy access to schools, shopping, and more, it's a rare find. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the charm of this property for yourself. Welcome to a lifetime of memories waiting to be made!
